nodes.text: De-hoff Greenly was one of two sisters of Tag Greenley. She, like her other sibling Ta-mara, dated Lando Calrissian.
Lando had trouble double-booking them and Tag provided him with an alibi.
In 0 ABY, De-hoff was on Malastare dating Lando when she caught him with Senator Krystal's daughter. As a result, Tag fought in Lando's place in the Battle of Taanab to cover his absence.
